RcppArmadillo-package   R and Armadillo Integration
RcppArmadillo.package.skeleton
                        Create a skeleton for a new package that
                        intends to use RcppArmadillo
armadillo_set_seed      Set the Armadillo Random Number Generator to
                        the given value
armadillo_set_seed_random
                        Set the Armadillo Random Number Generator to a
                        random value
armadillo_version       Report the version of Armadillo
fastLm                  Bare-bones linear model fitting function
